## Summary

| You CAN | You CANNOT |
|---------|------------|
| Use the source code | Use for real financial services |
| Modify and distribute | Hold us liable for data exposure |
| Learn from the implementation | Expect production-level security |
| Build your own sandbox | Use outside SimToolBox ecosystem |
| Contribute improvements | Process real transactions |

